{
  "stem": "9446.2",
  "chunk_idx": 13,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 7.6,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And then I found myself in Ulm, which is Bavaria, southern part of Germany.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "By the way, Einstein was born in Ulm.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And Donau-- Donau was the name of the river-- in English, Danube. 'Blue Danube,' you've heard of the waltz, 'Blue Danube,' maybe?",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "That's in English.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And in German, it's Donau.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "So that town, Ulm, we were in that town, living.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "We were sent to a German barracks, former German Army barracks called Boelcke-Kaserne.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "If you want  me to spell that for you, I can do that.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "Boelcke is-- that's the name of the barracks, B-O-E-L-C-K-E dash Kaserne-- which means barracks-- K-A-S-E-R-N-E.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Now, it wasn't too bad there.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "They were-- those are former, you know, domiciles of the German soldiers.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And it wasn't too bad, except we were terribly crowded.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "But we had running water, even it was possible to take a bath there.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "[CHUCKLES] And so we were there through '46, '47.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I was working, by the way, in the employment office.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I was an employment officer.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Because a lot of our refugees were employed by the UNRRA.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "UNRRA was an organization, as I mentioned to you, the international United Nations Refugee organization.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "It was under the American control.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And they wanted people to help them.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] Mm-hm.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "OK?",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "Just finish what you were saying there.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And they wanted people to help them to organize employment office.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And I was one of them.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I was an employment officer.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "But it was all organized and sponsored by UNRRA, 1946. '47, actually, pretty much until we left for the United States, which was '49.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "We came--",
      "word_count": 2
    }
  ],
